# Commit Convention

## Format

```
<type>(<scope>): <subject>

Body explanation — what + why (not how, code self-evident)

Co-reviewed-by: <sub-agent> (PASS/details)
Refs: <vault ref> (lock-in date)
```

## Types
- `feat`: new feature
- `fix`: bug fix
- `chore`: build / config / housekeeping
- `docs`: documentation only
- `refactor`: code restructure without behavior change
- `test`: test add / update
- `perf`: performance improvement
- `style`: formatting (no code change)
- `build`: build system / external deps
- `ci`: CI config / scripts

## Scopes (cohort 정합)
- `w3-thu-cascade` / `w3-fri` / `w4-mon-tue` / `w4-wed` / `w4-thu` / `w4-fri` / `w5-mon-tue` / `w5-wed` / `w5-thu` / `w5-fri`
- `aurora` / `vesper` / `safety` / `payment` / `auth` / `viral` / `cache` / `survey` / `shape-c` / `nudge` / `landing` / `dashboard`

## Co-reviewed-by attribution
모든 commit 영역 sub-agent dispatch 결과 명시:
```
Co-reviewed-by: cohort-design-system (PASS — 8 dim), cohort-accessibility-auditor (PASS — 8 dim), cohort-product (PASS — 7 dim), safety-filter-tester (PASS — 50+ test case)
```

## Vault refs

Spec decision 영역 vault ref 명시 의무:
```
Refs: vault 56 §6 D14, vault 62 §2.1 (CEO confirm 2026-05-25), vault 38 §2.2
```

## Anti-pattern guard

- AO-4: `--no-verify` BANNED — fix hook root cause
- Body explanation 영역 *why* > *what* > *how* priority
